OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOfgem blamed as supplier   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffailures lead to higher    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fenergy bills               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy watchdog Ofgem has been accused 
OL,6, of allowing an industry to develop on  
OL,7, "shaky foundations" in which a series  
OL,8, of supply companies collapsed.         
OL,10,FAll billpayers are paying about #94    
OL,11,Fmore each to cover the #2.7bn cost of  
OL,12,Fthe failure of 28 suppliers which      
OL,13,Ffolded after wholesale prices soared.  
OL,15,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said   
OL,16,FOfgem had allowed a market to develop  
OL,17,Fthat was vulnerable to large shocks.   
OL,19,FThe regulator said it was already      
OL,20,Faddressing the issues raised.          
